data.description: Absolutely beautiful and highly sought-after Ranch Home with a large, covered Rocking Chair front porch. The backyard is large and fenced. Great mountain views from the front porch! You will enjoy mornings and evenings on the private and peaceful Screened Porch. This home is well maintained and one of the nicest homes in the subdivision in my opinion. The Kitchen offers Granite Counter tops, Lots of counter space and Gas appliances. Lots of Crown molding and high ceilings. Beautiful LVP Flooring. The Owner's suite offers a large shower, double vanity, walk in closet and trayed ceiling. Large 2 car garage with lots of space. Close to I575, shopping and restaurants. The HOA mows the yard!
